# day 02-services & Tags

  ## Ansible -Install & enable Nginx

  ---
  -name: install and start Nginx on linux servers
  Hosts: all
  become: yes

    tasks:
       -name: install nginx
        yum:
            name:nginx 
            state: present

            -name: enable nginx
            service:
               name: nginx
               state: started
                 enabled: yes


                   
